***quotes***

"In almost any subject, your passion for the subject will save you 
 If you care enough for the result you will most certainly attain it.
 If you wish to be good, you will be good.
 If you wish to be rich, you will be rich.
 If you wish to be learned, you will be learned.
 
 Only then you must really wish these things and wish them
 exclusiveness and not wish one hundred other incompatible things
 just as strongly."
					by William James, Harvard Uninversity.

